 * Installing on Linux and other platforms

INSTALLING ON LINUX AND OTHER PLATFORMS
=======================================

Download and install Python 2.5 or higher from
http://www.python.org/download/.

Download the latest version of BB platform from http://bionicbunny.org
to the place where it will live (e.g. /opt/bionicbunny/). Go to this
directory and run install.py script from the root as follows:

 $ sudo install.py

or

 $ sudo make install